TI  - DIVERGING TESTS OF EQUAL PREDICTIVE ABILITY
AU  - McCracken, Michael W.
AB  - [We investigate claims made in Giacomini and White (2006) and Diebold (2015) regarding the asymptotic normality of a test of equal predictive ability. A counterexample is provided in which, instead, the test statistic diverges with probability 1 under the null.]
